00:18:46.789 --> 00:18:47.789
&gt;&gt;Jerry: Ah.

00:18:47.789 --> 00:18:51.600
&gt;&gt;male #1: And I gotta ask, "Police Squad"
obviously led into "Naked Gun."

00:18:51.600 --> 00:18:54.670
