00:24:43.750 --> 00:24:51.571
There is sometimes, you know, I never want
to say this to a studio, but there is some

00:24:51.571 --> 00:24:55.750
creativity gained to a lower budget.

00:24:55.750 --> 00:24:57.970
Having to do things for less money.

00:24:57.970 --> 00:25:03.070
And by the way, it depends upon the kind of
movie you're making.

00:25:03.070 --> 00:25:12.769
I mean, if you're making one of these special
effects movies with a huge landscape, then

00:25:12.769 --> 00:25:16.870
I don't know if Avatar would have been helped
by a smaller budget.

00:25:16.870 --> 00:25:18.130
[laughter]

00:25:18.130 --> 00:25:25.040
