you can work with.

00:25:32.169 --> 00:25:35.049
At the time, for us, we didn't even get--.

00:25:35.049 --> 00:25:36.679
The number meant nothing to us.

00:25:36.679 --> 00:25:38.549
I mean three million dollars seemed like a
lot.

00:25:38.549 --> 00:25:43.600
That's a lot of money.

00:25:43.600 --> 00:25:46.750
And we were just thrilled to get out there
and make the movie.

00:25:46.750 --> 00:25:52.320
And we, Jon Davison, who is one of the producers
who is, and Howard Koch.

00:25:52.320 --> 00:25:57.480
We just trust that they kind of, they would
just say "OK, you've gotta do this.

00:25:57.480 --> 00:26:01.640
Shoot this scene in a half a day and this
scene and do you think you can do this and

00:26:01.640 --> 00:26:02.640
that.

00:26:02.640 --> 00:26:04.410
