balanced.

00:38:23.240 --> 00:38:24.240
&gt;&gt;Jerry: Uh.

00:38:24.240 --> 00:38:25.240
Yeah.

00:38:25.240 --> 00:38:26.490
I don't think we did that purposefully.

00:38:26.490 --> 00:38:29.619
I mean, 'cause we weren't t thinking.

