Because what they did is, we didn't, once
again low budget.

00:55:01.320 --> 00:55:06.339
There really was only one that did the main
one that was used.

00:55:06.339 --> 00:55:13.130
The second one was only for, it was like a
more of a balloon.

00:55:13.130 --> 00:55:15.809
Like a little bit more like this kind of thing.

00:55:15.809 --> 00:55:22.680
Where when she, when it takes it out, when
it's released from its seat, and it's sort

00:55:22.680 --> 00:55:25.809
of grabbing her and stuff like that.

00:55:25.809 --> 00:55:35.809
That, but, the one that I have was the Auto,
but at the, it's repainted to the female face

00:55:35.809 --> 00:55:38.550
for the end of the film.

00:55:38.550 --> 00:55:44.160
But that was a clever deal that they, I mean,
they made the head swivel, and they figured

00:55:44.160 --> 00:55:47.420
out how to make it bounce up and down and
all that stuff.

00:55:47.420 --> 00:55:50.830
So that was, Auto was fun.

